+  1. Basic FIFO queue with UUID generation and status tracking
+  2. Named queues with independent task lists
+  3. Priority-based ordering (1-10, lower = higher priority)
+  4. Delayed/scheduled tasks with `delay` and `runAt` options
+  5. Retry with exponential backoff (`backoffMs * 2^(attempt-1)`)
