+  8. Per-queue concurrency control
+  9. Progress tracking and task cancellation
+  10. Cron-based recurring tasks (`*/N * * * *`, `0 * * * *`, `0 0 * * *`)
+  11. Middleware pipeline with `use()` and `process()`
+  12. Graceful shutdown with timeout and force-cancel
